            <lg xml:id="TK1312">
<l>ūṭi yiruntēmāt tummiṉār yāntammai </l>
<l>nīṭuvāḻ keṉpa taṟintu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I continued to be sulky he sneezed and thought I would (then) wish him a long life.</l>
